#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.merge.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.merge"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:1 of
msgid "Merge DataFrame or named Series objects with a database-style join."
msgstr "使用数据库风格的连接合并 DataFrame 或命名的 Series 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:3 of
msgid ""
"A named Series object is treated as a DataFrame with a single named "
"column."
msgstr "命名的 Series 对象被视为具有单个命名列的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:5 of
msgid ""
"The join is done on columns or indexes. If joining columns on columns, "
"the DataFrame indexes *will be ignored*. Otherwise if joining indexes on "
"indexes or indexes on a column or columns, the index will be passed on. "
"When performing a cross merge, no column specifications to merge on are "
"allowed."
msgstr ""
"连接操作在列或索引上进行。如果按列连接列，则 DataFrame 的索引*将被忽略*。"
"否则，如果按索引连接索引，或将索引与列连接，则索引会被保留。执行交叉合并"
"时，不允许指定用于合并的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:11 of
msgid "Object to merge with."
msgstr "要合并的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:13 of
msgid ""
"Type of merge to be performed.  * left: use only keys from left frame, "
"similar to a SQL left outer join;   preserve key order. * right: use only"
" keys from right frame, similar to a SQL right outer join;   preserve key"
" order. * outer: use union of keys from both frames, similar to a SQL "
"full outer   join; sort keys lexicographically. * inner: use intersection"
" of keys from both frames, similar to a SQL inner   join; preserve the "
"order of the left keys."
msgstr ""
"要执行的合并类型。  * left：仅使用左表的键，类似于 SQL 的左外连接；保留键"
"的顺序。 * right：仅使用右表的键，类似于 SQL 的右外连接；保留键的顺序。 *"
" outer：使用两个表中键的并集，类似于 SQL 的全外连接；按键的字典序排序。 *"
" inner：使用两个表中键的交集，类似于 SQL 的内连接；保留左键的顺序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:13 of
msgid "Type of merge to be performed."
msgstr "要执行的合并类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:15 of
msgid ""
"left: use only keys from left frame, similar to a SQL left outer join; "
"preserve key order."
msgstr "left：仅使用左框架的键，类似于 SQL 左外连接；保持键的顺序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:17 of
msgid ""
"right: use only keys from right frame, similar to a SQL right outer join;"
" preserve key order."
msgstr "right：仅使用右框架的键，类似于 SQL 右外连接；保持键的顺序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:19 of
msgid ""
"outer: use union of keys from both frames, similar to a SQL full outer "
"join; sort keys lexicographically."
msgstr ""
"outer：使用两个框架的键的并集，类似于 SQL 全外连接；按字典顺序对键进行"
"排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:21 of
msgid ""
"inner: use intersection of keys from both frames, similar to a SQL inner "
"join; preserve the order of the left keys."
msgstr "inner：使用两个框架的键的交集，类似于 SQL 内连接；保持左键的顺序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:24 of
msgid ""
"Column or index level names to join on. These must be found in both "
"DataFrames. If `on` is None and not merging on indexes then this defaults"
" to the intersection of the columns in both DataFrames."
msgstr ""
"用于连接的列或索引级别名称。这些名称必须在两个 DataFrame 中都存在。如果 `"
"on` 为 None 且未按索引合并，则默认为两个 DataFrame 中列的交集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:28 of
msgid ""
"Column or index level names to join on in the left DataFrame. Can also be"
" an array or list of arrays of the length of the left DataFrame. These "
"arrays are treated as if they are columns."
msgstr ""
"左 DataFrame 中用于连接的列或索引级别名称。也可以是长度与左 DataFrame "
"相同的数组或数组列表。这些数组将被视为列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:32 of
msgid ""
"Column or index level names to join on in the right DataFrame. Can also "
"be an array or list of arrays of the length of the right DataFrame. These"
" arrays are treated as if they are columns."
msgstr ""
"右 DataFrame 中用于连接的列或索引级别名称。也可以是长度与右 DataFrame "
"相同的数组或数组列表。这些数组将被视为列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:36 of
msgid ""
"Use the index from the left DataFrame as the join key(s). If it is a "
"MultiIndex, the number of keys in the other DataFrame (either the index "
"or a number of columns) must match the number of levels."
msgstr ""
"使用左 DataFrame 的索引作为连接键。如果是 MultiIndex，则另一个 DataFrame "
"中的键数量（无论是索引还是列）必须与级别数匹配。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:40 of
msgid ""
"Use the index from the right DataFrame as the join key. Same caveats as "
"left_index."
msgstr "使用右 DataFrame 的索引作为连接键。注意事项与 left_index 相同。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:43 of
msgid ""
"Sort the join keys lexicographically in the result DataFrame. If False, "
"the order of the join keys depends on the join type (how keyword)."
msgstr ""
"在结果 DataFrame 中按键的字典序排序连接键。如果为 False，则连接键的顺序"
"取决于连接类型（how 关键字）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:46 of
msgid ""
"A length-2 sequence where each element is optionally a string indicating "
"the suffix to add to overlapping column names in `left` and `right` "
"respectively. Pass a value of `None` instead of a string to indicate that"
" the column name from `left` or `right` should be left as-is, with no "
"suffix. At least one of the values must not be None."
msgstr ""
"长度为 2 的序列，其中每个元素可选为一个字符串，表示要分别添加到 `left` 和"
" `right` 中重叠列名的后缀。传递 `None` 而不是字符串表示该列名应保持原样，"
"不添加后缀。至少有一个值不能为 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:53 of
msgid "If False, avoid copy if possible."
msgstr "如果为 False，则尽可能避免复制。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:55 of
msgid ""
"If True, adds a column to the output DataFrame called \"_merge\" with "
"information on the source of each row. The column can be given a "
"different name by providing a string argument. The column will have a "
"Categorical type with the value of \"left_only\" for observations whose "
"merge key only appears in the left DataFrame, \"right_only\" for "
"observations whose merge key only appears in the right DataFrame, and "
"\"both\" if the observation's merge key is found in both DataFrames."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则向输出 DataFrame 添加一个名为 \"_merge\" 的列，其中包含"
"每行来源的信息。可以通过提供字符串参数为该列指定不同的名称。该列将具有"
"分类类型，其值为：\"left_only\" 表示合并键仅出现在左 DataFrame 中的观测，"
"\"right_only\" 表示合并键仅出现在右 DataFrame 中的观测，\"both\" 表示合并"
"键在两个 DataFrame 中都存在。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:63 of
msgid ""
"If specified, checks if merge is of specified type.  * \"one_to_one\" or "
"\"1:1\": check if merge keys are unique in both   left and right "
"datasets. * \"one_to_many\" or \"1:m\": check if merge keys are unique in"
" left   dataset. * \"many_to_one\" or \"m:1\": check if merge keys are "
"unique in right   dataset. * \"many_to_many\" or \"m:m\": allowed, but "
"does not result in checks."
msgstr ""
"如果指定，则检查合并是否为指定类型。  * \"one_to_one\" 或 \"1:1\"：检查"
"合并键在左右两个数据集中是否唯一。 * \"one_to_many\" 或 \"1:m\"：检查合并"
"键在左数据集中是否唯一。 * \"many_to_one\" 或 \"m:1\"：检查合并键在右数据"
"集中是否唯一。 * \"many_to_many\" 或 \"m:m\"：允许，但不会执行检查。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:63 of
msgid "If specified, checks if merge is of specified type."
msgstr "如果指定，则检查合并是否为指定类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:65 of
msgid ""
"\"one_to_one\" or \"1:1\": check if merge keys are unique in both left "
"and right datasets."
msgstr "\"one_to_one\" 或 \"1:1\"：检查合并键在左数据集和右数据集中是否唯一。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:67 of
msgid ""
"\"one_to_many\" or \"1:m\": check if merge keys are unique in left "
"dataset."
msgstr "\"one_to_many\" 或 \"1:m\"：检查合并键在左数据集中是否唯一。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:69 of
msgid ""
"\"many_to_one\" or \"m:1\": check if merge keys are unique in right "
"dataset."
msgstr "\"many_to_one\" 或 \"m:1\"：检查合并键在右数据集中是否唯一。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:71 of
msgid "\"many_to_many\" or \"m:m\": allowed, but does not result in checks."
msgstr "\"many_to_many\" 或 \"m:m\"：允许，但不会进行检查。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:73 of
msgid ""
"\"broadcast\" is recommended when one DataFrame is much smaller than the "
"other, otherwise, \"shuffle\" will be a better choice. By default, we "
"choose method according to actual data size."
msgstr ""
"当一个 DataFrame 比另一个小得多时，推荐使用 \"broadcast\"，否则 \"shuffle"
"\" 是更好的选择。默认情况下，我们根据实际数据大小选择方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:77 of
msgid ""
"Auto merge small chunks before or after merge  * \"both\": auto merge "
"small chunks before and after, * \"none\": do not merge small chunks * "
"\"before\": only merge small chunks before merge * \"after\": only merge "
"small chunks after merge"
msgstr ""
"在合并前或合并后自动合并小块  * \"both\"：在合并前后都自动合并小块， * \""
"none\"：不合并小块 * \"before\"：仅在合并前合并小块 * \"after\"：仅在合并"
"后合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:77 of
msgid "Auto merge small chunks before or after merge"
msgstr "在合并之前或之后自动合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:79 of
msgid "\"both\": auto merge small chunks before and after,"
msgstr "\"both\"：在合并之前和之后自动合并小块，"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:80 of
msgid "\"none\": do not merge small chunks"
msgstr "\"none\"：不合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:81 of
msgid "\"before\": only merge small chunks before merge"
msgstr "\"before\"：仅在合并之前合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:82 of
msgid "\"after\": only merge small chunks after merge"
msgstr "\"after\"：仅在合并之后合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:84 of
msgid ""
"When how is \"inner\", merged result could be much smaller than original "
"DataFrame, if the number of chunks is greater than the threshold, it will"
" merge small chunks automatically."
msgstr ""
"当 how 为 \"inner\" 时，合并结果可能远小于原始 DataFrame，如果块数量超过"
"阈值，它将自动合并小块。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:88 of
msgid "Use bloom filter to optimize merge"
msgstr "使用布隆过滤器优化合并"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:90 of
msgid ""
"* \"max_elements\": max elements in bloom filter,   default value is the "
"max size of all input chunks * \"error_rate\": error raite, default 0.1. "
"* \"apply_chunk_size_threshold\": min chunk size of input chunks to apply"
" bloom filter, default 10   when chunk size of left and right is greater "
"than this threshold, apply bloom filter * \"filter\": \"large\", "
"\"small\", \"both\", default \"large\"   decides to filter on large, "
"small or both DataFrames."
msgstr ""
"* \"max_elements\"：布隆过滤器中的最大元素数，默认值为所有输入块的最大"
"大小\n"
"* \"error_rate\"：错误率，默认 0.1\n"
"* \"apply_chunk_size_threshold\"：应用布隆过滤器的最小块大小阈值，默认 10"
"\n"
"  当左右 DataFrame 的块大小大于此阈值时，应用布隆过滤器\n"
"* \"filter\"：\"large\"、\"small\"、\"both\"，默认 \"large\"\n"
"  决定对大、小或两个 DataFrame 进行过滤"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:91 of
msgid ""
"\"max_elements\": max elements in bloom filter, default value is the max "
"size of all input chunks"
msgstr "\"max_elements\"：布隆过滤器中的最大元素数，默认值为所有输入块的最大大小"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:93 of
msgid "\"error_rate\": error raite, default 0.1."
msgstr "\"error_rate\"：错误率，默认 0.1"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:94 of
msgid ""
"\"apply_chunk_size_threshold\": min chunk size of input chunks to apply "
"bloom filter, default 10 when chunk size of left and right is greater "
"than this threshold, apply bloom filter"
msgstr ""
"\"apply_chunk_size_threshold\"：应用布隆过滤器的最小块大小阈值，默认 10\n"
"当左右 DataFrame 的块大小大于此阈值时，应用布隆过滤器"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:96 of
msgid ""
"\"filter\": \"large\", \"small\", \"both\", default \"large\" decides to "
"filter on large, small or both DataFrames."
msgstr ""
"\"filter\"：\"large\"、\"small\"、\"both\"，默认 \"large\"，决定对大、小"
"或两个 DataFrame 进行过滤"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:99 of
msgid ""
"Join strategy to use for left frame. When data skew occurs, consider "
"these strategies to avoid long-tail issues, but use them cautiously to "
"prevent OOM and unnecessary overhead."
msgstr ""
"左表使用的连接策略。当出现数据倾斜时，考虑使用这些策略避免长尾问题，但请"
"谨慎使用以防止 OOM 和不必要的开销。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:102 of
msgid "Join strategy to use for right frame."
msgstr "右表使用的连接策略。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:105 of
msgid "A DataFrame of the two merged objects."
msgstr "两个合并对象的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:109 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:128 of
msgid ""
"Merge df1 and df2 on the lkey and rkey columns. The value columns have "
"the default suffixes, _x and _y, appended."
msgstr "基于 lkey 和 rkey 列合并 df1 和 df2。值列附加默认后缀 _x 和 _y。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:140 of
msgid ""
"Merge DataFrames df1 and df2 with specified left and right suffixes "
"appended to any overlapping columns."
msgstr "合并 DataFrame df1 和 df2，并为任何重叠列附加指定的左右后缀。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.merge:153 of
msgid ""
"Merge DataFrames df1 and df2, but raise an exception if the DataFrames "
"have any overlapping columns."
msgstr "合并 DataFrame df1 和 df2，但如果 DataFrame 有任何重叠列，则抛出异常。"

